tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mark-lanegans-estate-announces-bubblegum-20th-anniversary-box-set-3773381"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>您可以<a href="https://shop.beggarsarkive.com/release/463840-mark-lanegan-bubblegum-xx" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>了解有关“Bubblegum XX”的更多信息并进行预订。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-previously-unreleased-mark-lanegan-song-heard-a-train-3781052">聆听马克·兰根 (Mark Lanegan) 之前未发行的歌曲“Heard A Train”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
